      <div class="featured-eyebrow">Programme</div>
      <h2>Final Programme</h2>
      <p>
        The Annual Conference is structured around two categories of panels, in addition to poster
        sessions. <strong>"Closed panels"</strong> are recurring year-over-year and are pre-established
        by the EISS. <strong>"Open panels"</strong> are proposed by participants.
      </p>
      <figure style="margin: var(--space-5) 0 0; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow: hidden;">
